_sText:
This is my first fy_ map and it is my second map I ever made, I spent about 5 - 7 hours making this. 

You start in an house and you go through a tunnel and outside, outside there is bridge to the other side of the map ( The opponent's side ) or you can go into the teleport ( The door frame ) and go up to the sky house, from there you go outside to the balcony and you can climb up the ladder and walk around the top of the map.

I still want to improve it and it is a beta, so please give some comments that will help me improve this map.

Updated.

The box in the middle is a trap, If you go into a teleport you will be trapped in the glass box :D
